Dialogue: 0,-1:59:54.27,-1:59:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspense and deduction closes the gap between
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:56.33,-1:59:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The love and hatred between two people.
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:58.14,-1:59:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mysteries abound. Strange events
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.87,0:00:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan and Heiji. What will Jodie do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.74,0:00:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nofcase is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori and I have some doubts that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie, the teacher, belongs to the Black organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to Jodie's room to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:02:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we encountered an unexpected incident at the entrance of her condominium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,falling from above?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man came falling from the 21st floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had the front door been locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! lilt was locked up tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this room was locked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it must be suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is what I first thought too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I saw the curtain of the bedroom window
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from where Mr. Takai jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain was tagged down and the curtain rail was bent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a few hooks came off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This shows evidence that he involuntarily grabbed the curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he came close to falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would someone trying to kill himself do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, then this is not suicide but in fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a homicide case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,English Teacher v.s.\NRenowned Detective of the West" Part II
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cont
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's also a murder in a locked room,\Nlike we so often see in novels or movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. Jodie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why ae you ere anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My room is next door to Mr. Takai's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two just came to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just when we were leaving the building to go out for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takai came falling down in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So have you solved this locked room murder mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think the strange mark on the window glass
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,may have something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a mark like something hit it from outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've finished developing the pictures that Ms. Shimoda took.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most are just ordinary photos of the building
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there was aypicture with a strange figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we blew up the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Ma Takai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He grabbed the curtain after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's throwing something into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, then, he threw the cellphone at the window and made the mark on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he throw it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a call made him very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is police business!\NYou civilians, don't belong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, talk about hot tempered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was going 0 ep im UU no anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm fed up with those guys.\NHow could this happen to me so frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, although it's true that they may be annoying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for some reason, with them around, the case is usually solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know in what way the culprit lead\NMr. Takai to jump from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All Ms. Shimoda could've done was hock him with the flash of his camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was nothing strange about the mail that Mr. Nakamachi sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one left is Mr. Kawakami, who called him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would jump to death from the window only because he's told to do so, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another thing that bothers me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the reason why he threw the cell phone into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A plausible explanation could be that he left a clue in his cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he didn't want it to drop and break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the cell phone didn't break even If 1tifell
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there were no suspicious letters on the screen either...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,WHAT TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IS IT NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time do you think it is now, you dumb dork!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've completely forgotten to meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing. Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said that you wanted to go try out the delicious restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that Mr. Ootaki told you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry but I don't think I'll make it today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji! Where're you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H... I'm in a weak signal a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!? Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H... I can't get to where you from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... Tokyo. I'm in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to get back to you as soon as I finished what I had to do but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, saidiwe'd meet in front of the Big Man of Umeda, at 7 o'clock tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wrote it down in my memo too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,fl see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's what it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the murderer is that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? An experiment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we reenact what the three did before\NMr. Takai fell to his death from the 2187 floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may be able to solve the mystery of the locked room murder quite easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Shimoda was only taking photos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Mr. Nakamachi was only sending mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that Mr. Kawakami, in his drunken state,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,cursed Mr. Takai on the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's far from murder
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. Let's give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,yin order to carry out the experiment, we're missing some things
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Missing some things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liquor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, Mr. Takai fell asleep drunk before he fell to his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who's going to play the role of the drunk victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the problem...\NThe police officer can't drink on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm under age
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person who can play the role is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Jodie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you play the role of the drunk victim for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on one condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you prepare my favorite liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, good!
